int convert_arpa( int in )
    converts an IP number to it's .in-addr.arpa format
    ex: 141.211.231.10 -> 10.231.211.141.in-addr.arpa

Set default QTYPE and QCLASS to 0

char * dnsr_errorstr( DNSR dnsr )
    looks at the error code and returns an error message.

void dnsr_close( DNSR dnsr )
    closes a DNSR opened with dnsr_open

API:

want as few calls as possible

